snippet.title: Need for Speed: ProStreet - Pepega Edition | Story Trailer
snippet.description:
After Ryan Cooper's fall from grace you step into the shoes of Nick, his unsuccessful cousin, trying to turn his life around. Enter a world of racing legends and uncover the dark underbelly of the racing scene. Thankfully you won't be alone - Eden, staff of the festival event, will help you along the way. Can you claim the title back to the 'Cooper' name and purge the festival of corruption?
▼ MORE INFO DOWN BELOW ▼

Learn more about the next Pepega Mod on our Discord Server: https://discord.com/invite/YbFadBv
Car Audio Gameplay Showcase: https://youtu.be/Rv75Qirc6Zw
Announcement Trailer: https://youtu.be/FkdLLqna0k8

Trailer Song: Timbaland - Miscommunication (The Bloody Beetroots Remix)
Thank you to SerbianMods for parts of the Golf model!
